<h1><strong> Sweepstakes Terms and Conditions:</strong></h1>
Five  random (5) EMF (Essence Music Festival) Twitter followers on Twitter.com (For  avoidance of doubt, the Twitter users who follow EMF on Twitter.com) (each, a  &quot;Winner&quot; and collectively, the &quot;Winners&quot;) who re-tweet the  EMF tweet about the &quot; For a chance 2 win an exclusive collectors CD/DVD  from EMF &amp; Music World RT. #EMF2010 <a href="http://bit.ly/emf15th">http://bit.ly/emf15th</a>"on  Twitter.com located at <a href="http://www.twitter.com/essencemusic">http://www.twitter.com/essencemusic</a> will each receive: a  collector’s item  15th  Anniversary Essence Music Festival Vol 2.1 CD/DVD  from Essence Music Festival &amp; Music World  five (5) Prizes will be available, one (1) per Winner for a total of five (5)  Winners.
<br/><br/>
This  Giveaway starts at 12:00:00PM ET on June 28, 2010 and expires at 12:00:00 PM ET  on June 29, 2010 (the &quot;Giveaway Period&quot;). During the Giveaway Period,  follow EMF on Twitter at http://www.twitter.com/essencemusic. Once EMF  announces when to start re-tweeting, start re-tweeting (the &quot;Re-Tweeting  Period&quot;) EMF's tweet about the Sweepstakes. The Re-Tweeting Period will  continue until the end of the Sweepstakes Period.<br/><br/>

How to participate in the EMF Sweepstakes for a chance to win a Prize:

<ul>
	<li>Go to <a href="">http://www.twitter.com/essencemusic</a> and follow EMF.</li>
	<li>Once EMF on Twitter announces the Re-Tweeting Period has started, re-tweet EMF's tweet about the Giveaway from your Twitter account to all of your followers in this format: <strong>
	&quot;For  a chance 2 win an exclusive collectors CD/DVD from EMF &amp; Music World RT.  #EMF2010 <a href="http://bit.ly/emf15th">http://bit.ly/emf15th</a>".</strong></li>
	<li>Check your Twitter direct messages on or around  June 30, 2010 to see if you are a Winner.</li>
	<li>If you are a Winner, EMF will direct message you at your Twitter account that re-tweeted the winning tweet to let you know that you are a Winner.</li>
	<li>Winners will have one (1) week to reply and  provide a valid mailing address in order for EMF (as defined herein) to mail  you the Prize. Anyone who does not reply with their mailing address by July 9,  2010 will be disqualified and the fifth (6th) person to re-tweet EMF's tweet  will be a Winner. The process will repeat itself until four (5) Winners have  been notified and have replied with their mailing address. Minors should obtain  their parent's permission and assistance prior to sending EMF their mailing  address. By emailing your mailing address to EMF, you (or your parent/guardian  if you are a minor) agree to these terms and conditions (&quot;Terms&quot;). Do  not email EMF your mailing address if you disagree with any of these Terms.</li>
	<li>	Each potential Winner will be required to sign (his/her parent/legal guardian must sign if potential Winner is not the age of majority in the jurisdiction in which he/she resides): (a) an affidavit of eligibility and release of EMF and its respective officers, directors, employees, agents and members, from any and all liability, loss, claims, demands, and causes of action for personal injury and/or damage, theft, loss, or any other harm suffered in connection with this giveaway or the use/misuse or acceptance of the Prize or any portion thereof to be eligible for the Prize; and (b) except where prohibited by law, a promotional release granting EMF the right to use his/her name, voice and likeness for advertising and publicity purposes without additional compensation and (c) any other documentation required by EMF, including a W2 form and Winner's social security number for tax purposes.</li>
</ul>
Sweepstakes  open to legal residents of the fifty (50) United States and District of  Columbia who are 14 years and older (except for legal residents of Maine who  must be 18 years of age or older), have a Twitter.com account, follow EMF on  Twitter and who re-tweet the exact tweet about &quot; For a chance 2 win an  exclusive collectors CD/DVD from EMF &amp; Music World RT. #EMF2010 <a href="http://bit.ly/emf15th">http://bit.ly/emf15th</a>"from  EMF's Twitter account. Employees and their immediate families (i.e., parents,  spouse, children, siblings, grandparents, step parents, step children and step  siblings) of EMF and its affiliated companies, sponsors, subsidiaries,  advertising agencies and third party fulfillment agencies (collectively, with  EMF, the &quot;Sweepstakes Entities&quot;) are not eligible to enter this  Promotion. Giveaway void where taxed, prohibited or restricted by law. If you  are already a Winner, you are ineligible to win again. Only one (1) prize per  person - per Twitter account. Only one (1) re-tweet per person- per Twitter  account. If you re-tweet multiple times, only the first re-tweet will be  counted.<br/><br/>
<p>Participation in this  Giveaway constitutes agreement that EMF and all related parties involved in  this Giveaway, are not responsible or liable for:</p>
<ol>
	<li>electronic transmissions or submissions that are lost, late, stolen, incomplete, illegible, damaged, garbled, destroyed, or misdirected; </li>
	<li>any problems or technical malfunctions, errors, omissions, interruptions, deletions, defects, delays in operation of transmission, communication failures, destruction or unauthorized access to, or alteration of, submissions; or</li>
	<li>failed or unavailable hardware, network, software or telephone transmissions, damage to offer participant's or any person's computer and/or its contents, or causes beyond Sponsor's reasonable control that jeopardize the administration, security, fairness, integrity or proper conduct of this Giveaway. If for any reason this Giveaway cannot be executed as planned, including but not limited to infection by computer virus, bugs, tampering, unauthorized intervention, fraud, technical failures, or any other causes beyond the control of Sponsor that corrupt or affect the security, administration, fairness, integrity or proper conduct of this Giveaway or if this Giveaway is compromised or becomes technically corrupted in any way, electronically or otherwise, Sponsor reserves the right to terminate or suspend the Giveaway. By participating in this Giveaway, each participant (or his/her parent or legal guardian if participant is a minor) agrees to release and hold harmless the Sweepstakes Entities of each of the foregoing, from and against any and all liability arising from or in connection with participation in the Giveaway and/or the use of the Prize, including but not limited to, liability arising from or in connection with third-party claims. This Giveaway is made by EMF.</li>
</ol>
